<subSubSection id="C36E651149180D27FF1ABB79FD30F9E4" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BCB369A49180D27FF1ABB79FD30F9E4" blockId="4.[136,787,1378,1594]" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FF1ABB79FF77FAA4" box="[174,233,1378,1401]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">Notes</emphasis>
. – 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949180D27FEBBBB79FE51FAA7" box="[271,463,1378,1402]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lepidoziaceae" genus="Bazzania" kingdom="Plantae" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="gracilis">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FEBBBB79FE51FAA7" box="[271,463,1378,1402]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">Bazzania gracilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a widespread neotropical species characterized by the small plants (
<quantity id="4C8C9B7F49180D27FDDFBB99FD55FA44" box="[619,715,1409,1434]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" unit="mm" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1 – 2 mm</quantity>
wide) with strongly caducous, entire to shallowly 2-lobed leaves (GRADSTEIN, 2017). 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949180D27FEC4BBD9FD66FA07" authority="Steph." authorityName="Steph." box="[368,760,1474,1498]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lepidoziaceae" genus="Mastigobryum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="heterophyllum">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FEC4BBD9FD36FA07" box="[368,680,1474,1498]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">Mastigobryum heterophyllum</emphasis>
Steph.
</taxonomicName>
is identical to 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949180D27FEB1BBF9FEF9FA27" box="[261,359,1506,1530]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lepidoziaceae" genus="Bazzania" kingdom="Plantae" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="gracilis">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FEB1BBF9FEF9FA27" box="[261,359,1506,1530]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">B. gracilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. M. H. Fulford (in sched.) already noted this synonymy, but subsequently published 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949180D27FDFDB819FD69F9C7" box="[585,759,1538,1562]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lepidoziaceae" genus="Mastigobryum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="heterophyllum">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FDFDB819FD69F9C7" box="[585,759,1538,1562]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">M. heterophyllum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D1949180D27FEAAB839FE01F9E7" box="[286,415,1570,1594]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lepidoziaceae" genus="Bazzania" kingdom="Plantae" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" phylum="Marchantiophyta" rank="species" species="phyllobola">
<emphasis id="B900EA8849180D27FEAAB839FE01F9E7" box="[286,415,1570,1594]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="45">B. phyllobola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Spruce (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE54B6B49180D27FE4BB839FD3DF9E4" author="FULFORD, M. H." box="[511,675,1569,1594]" pageId="4" pageNumber="45" pagination="1 - 172" refId="ref7847" refString="FULFORD, M. H. (1963). Manual of the leafy Hepaticae of Latin America I. Mem. New York Bot. Gard. 11: 1 - 172." type="journal article" year="1963">FULFORD, 1963</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
